sketch.util.cli

Class CliOptionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.util.cli.CliOptionResult

  • public class CliOptionResult
extends java.lang.Object
    returns values for command line options. this is lazy in the sense that the command line will only be parsed when the first value is requested.
